er-mass (>~ 5 x 10^11 M_Sun) ACT\nresults show significantly less energy than predicted in the simulation\nincluding AGN feedback, while more closely matching the simulation without AGN\nfeedback, indicating that AGN feedback may be milder than often predicted in\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Nov 2017 20:15:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Aug 2018 04:13:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
